languages.text: "Вы правда считаете, что у меня есть время играть в ваши политические игры? С сожалением вынужден признать, что вы так до сих пор и не поняли, кто я такой и чем занимаюсь".
"Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."
languages.original_text: "Вы правда считаете, что у меня есть время играть в ваши политические игры? С сожалением вынужден признать, что вы так до сих пор и не поняли, кто я такой и чем занимаюсь".

traits.locale_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? I regret to admit that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."
"Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."
"Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."
"Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

languages.text: “莫非你真的以为，我有时间陪你玩你那些政治游戏吗？虽然很遗憾，但我必须承认，你还是不了解我是谁，也不了解我都在做些什么。”
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: “莫非你真的以为，我有时间陪你玩你那些政治游戏吗？虽然很遗憾，但我必须承认，你还是不了解我是谁，也不了解我都在做些什么。”

languages.text: «¿De verdad cree que tengo tiempo para sus juegos políticos? Admitiré con pesar que aún no entiende quién soy ni a qué me dedico».
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: «¿De verdad cree que tengo tiempo para sus juegos políticos? Admitiré con pesar que aún no entiende quién soy ni a qué me dedico».

languages.text: 「政治的駆け引きに興じる時間があると本気で思っているのか？残念だ、まだ私が何者で何を為すのか理解できていないのだな」
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: 「政治的駆け引きに興じる時間があると本気で思っているのか？残念だ、まだ私が何者で何を為すのか理解できていないのだな」

languages.text: « Vous pensez vraiment que j'ai le temps de m'adonner à vos petits jeux politiques ? Je suis au regret d'admettre que vous ne comprenez toujours pas qui je suis et ce que je fais. »
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: « Vous pensez vraiment que j'ai le temps de m'adonner à vos petits jeux politiques ? Je suis au regret d'admettre que vous ne comprenez toujours pas qui je suis et ce que je fais. »

languages.text: "Meint Ihr wirklich, ich hätte Zeit für Eure politischen Spiele? Leider muss ich erkennen, dass Ihr immer noch nicht begreift, wer ich bin und was ich tue."
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: "Meint Ihr wirklich, ich hätte Zeit für Eure politischen Spiele? Leider muss ich erkennen, dass Ihr immer noch nicht begreift, wer ich bin und was ich tue."

languages.text: "Politik oyunlarını oynayacak zamanım olduğunu mu sanıyorsun? Üzülerek belirtmeliyim ki kim olduğumu ve işimin ne olduğunu hâlâ tam olarak anlayamamışsın."
languages.original_text: "Do you really think that I have time to play your political games? With regret, I must concede that you still do not understand who I am and what I do."

traits.locale_text: "Senin o politik oyunlarını oynayacak zamanımın olduğunu mu sanıyorsun? Kim olduğumu ve işimin ne olduğunu hâlâ tam olarak anlamadığını üzülerek kabul etmem gerekiyor sanırım."
